---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import heroimage from '../media/retirementahead.jpg'
---

<section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-8 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8 lg:py-16 xl:gap-0">
    <div class="mr-auto place-self-center lg:col-span-7">
      <h1
        class="max-w-2xl text-4xl font-extrabold leading-none tracking-tight dark:text-white md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
      >
        Australian Independent Retirees (AIR)
      </h1>
      <h2
        class="mb-4 max-w-2xl text-2xl font-extrabold leading-none tracking-tight dark:text-white md:text-3xl xl:text-4xl"
      >
        Sydney Hills Branch
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mb-6 max-w-2xl font-light text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 md:text-lg lg:mb-8 lg:text-xl"
      >
        We regularly have a variety of interesting speakers/topics for our members and visitors. We
        hold 2 meetings on the 1st Friday of every month from February 2024 at the Beecroft
        Presbyterian Church Hall at 6a Welham St, Beecroft commencing at 10:45am.
      </p>
      <p
        class="mb-6 max-w-2xl font-light text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 md:text-lg lg:mb-8 lg:text-xl"
      >
        The first meeting covers a range of topics including Health, Aged Care, Travel, Technology,
        Retirement services, etc. After some refreshments, our second meeting at 12:30pm covers
        financial and investment topics including Superannuation, Retirement income, Investment
        Markets, Financial Trends, etc. If you are retired or approaching retirement, come along,
        meet new friends and receive about useful information to help your retirement.
      </p>
      <a
        href="http://independentretirees.com"
        class="dark:focus:ring-primary-900 mr-3 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-yellow-500 px-5 py-3 text-center text-base font-medium text-white hover:bg-yellow-600 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-yellow-300"
      >
        AIR National website
        <svg
          class="-mr-1 ml-2 h-5 w-5"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          ><path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
        >
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.facebook.com/independentretirees"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-gray-300 px-5 py-3 text-center text-base font-medium text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-100 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:focus:ring-gray-800"
      >
        Facebook page
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden lg:col-span-5 lg:mt-0 lg:flex">
      <Image src={heroimage} alt="Retirement Ahead" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
